      "releaseNotes": "• Fixed an issue that caused only a black screen to be displayed in certain cases\n\nThreema 7.2.4\n• Fixed a bug that could occur when opening chats\n• Fixed a bug that could occur when connecting to the server\n• Fixed a bug that occurred when deleting or editing sent messages\n• Various improvements related to VoiceOver and voice messages\n\nThreema 7.2.3\n• Fixed a bug related to restoring a Threema Safe backup with an own server\n\nThreema 7.2.1\n• Easy device switching: When switching to a new iPhone, Threema data can be transferred directly to the new device using Quick Start\n• Various performance optimizations\n• General improvements and various bug fixes\n\nThreema 7.2\n• Fixed several bugs related to the Liquid Glass design\n• Fixed several bugs related to individual and group calls\n• Fixed several bugs related to forwarding messages\n• Various performance optimizations\n• General improvements and various bug fixes",
